    "• Interpretation: Short documents stitched by us are likely be of unrelated topics.",
    "Hence, breakpoint-based chunking, which was given high hope by the LangChain and LlamaIndex communities, do not have an advantage for natively long documents.",
    "• Recommendation: Just use fixed-size chunking in practice.",
